abstract: >-
  Deterministic local evidence-surface scanner for bio and medical AI repositories.
  Produces reproducible T0-T4 review-priority tiers, a separate replication lane,
  evidence-ledger proof traces, provider-neutral advisory contract artifacts, and
  governed calibration-profile preview surfaces without requiring an LLM runtime.
